Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.50,0:00:56.09,tkopj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今日もこの胸は張り詰めたまま
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.70,0:01:03.04,tkopj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放学後に 約まれて 君を見てる Lady Lady
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.04,0:01:06.58,tkopj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ずっとあしらいは揃わないまま
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.27,0:01:13.76,tkopj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,続くから　内緒だよ　少し約め Lady Lady
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.23,0:01:16.84,tkopj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知りすぎて知らないから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.55,0:01:23.31,tkopj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聞こえないフリが上手になって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.79,0:01:28.56,tkopj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねぇ深呼吸一つしたら眼を開けて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.06,0:01:30.99,tkopj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自問自答やめて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.99,0:01:34.68,tkopj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何気なくおはようって言っちゃてる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.38,0:01:39.83,tkopj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飽きるくらい全部君がほしいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.83,0:01:42.27,tkopj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ハートは涙でいっぱい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.65,0:01:47.15,tkopj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋のいろはとがまた分かってないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.88,0:01:50.39,tkopj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何度も繰り返すけど
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.39,0:01:52.92,tkopj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寸前でまだ次回へ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.11,0:01:55.66,tkopj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,sweetな乙女心は
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.67,0:01:59.24,tkopj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あいにく取り扱ってないのです
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.24,0:02:01.69,tkopj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねぇ これが「I LOVE YOU」？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.50,0:00:56.09,tkopc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也是心中悸動不停
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.70,0:01:03.04,tkopc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放學後仍一直看著你 Lady Lady
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.04,0:01:06.58,tkopc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步調總是無法一致
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.27,0:01:13.76,tkopc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我還會繼續 這是秘密哦 一點點慢慢來 Lady Lady
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.23,0:01:16.84,tkopc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為太過瞭解而毫不知情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.55,0:01:23.31,tkopc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝聽不到也越裝越好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.79,0:01:28.56,tkopc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 深呼吸一次之後睜開眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.06,0:01:30.99,tkopc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在那自問自答了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.99,0:01:34.68,tkopc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若無其事地對他說「早上好」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.38,0:01:39.83,tkopc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要你的全部想要到自己都受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.83,0:01:42.27,tkopc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心中載滿淚水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.65,0:01:47.15,tkopc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不知道戀愛的顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.88,0:01:50.39,tkopc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論重複多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.39,0:01:52.92,tkopc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻總在最後一刻退縮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.11,0:01:55.66,tkopc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那甜甜的少女心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.67,0:01:59.24,tkopc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並沒有被操縱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.24,0:02:01.69,tkopc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說 這就是「I love you」?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.45,0:00:06.93,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.99,0:00:08.13,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 春
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.26,0:00:11.52,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雫　果然你家裏有什麼不該有的東西存在著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.53,0:00:12.01,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.18,0:00:17.31,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深夜總覺得睡不著 睜開眼睛以後
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.61,0:00:21.77,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在黑暗的地方 好像有個小孩站在那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.14,0:00:24.29,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直盯著我看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.66,0:00:28.11,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那是我弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.19,0:00:31.61,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煎雞蛋我要吃散的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.78,0:00:36.62,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 弟弟的性格和雫不怎麼像啊 叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.51,0:00:40.56,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 這怎麼搞得像你家一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.94,0:02:15.95,tk-title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(723,558)}暑  假
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.47,0:02:17.57,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.58,0:02:19.33,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又要補習了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.39,0:02:25.76,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田 他居然第一名
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.78,0:02:27.24,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是校方搞錯了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.89,0:02:30.56,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假的時候一定要好好的預習了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.16,0:02:33.64,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打起精神來啦 小水
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.75,0:02:37.26,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能考到689分已經很厲害啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.68,0:02:41.42,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像我這樣的全科目加起來連300分都沒到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.72,0:02:43.31,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定又要補考了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.97,0:02:45.31,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.43,0:03:01.87,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你穿比基尼的話我會很喜歡的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.89,0:03:03.34,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春同學 你真大膽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.22,0:03:06.43,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道你腦子裏在想什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.82,0:03:08.14,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我是不會去海邊玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.33,0:03:10.20,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.50,0:03:12.91,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把球技大會想參加的項目填好交上來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.90,0:03:15.65,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小水 你去哪裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.40,0:03:18.40,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對卷子上的題目還有疑問 去找老師問問
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.31,0:03:24.11,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不能在這些娛樂項目上提高點興趣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.37,0:03:26.61,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明有我這個好友在的說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.87,0:03:28.96,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許她壓根沒把你當朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.03,0:03:33.82,setting1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(168,64)\frz6.931}問題15
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.03,0:03:33.82,setting1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(557,93)\frz8.167}請用50個以內的文字簡單描述主人公此時此刻的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.03,0:03:33.82,setting2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz7.591\pos(821,294)}錯失嫁入豪門的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.03,0:03:33.82,setting2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz7.172\pos(890,421)}人生陷入絕望
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.82,0:03:32.85,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這道題目給我這個分？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.13,0:03:36.12,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我們已經下班了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.23,0:03:39.28,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師我現在沒心情看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.29,0:03:42.12,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還在上班時間內 請繼續工作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.75,0:03:45.34,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊這道題啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.48,0:03:48.86,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不是錯誤的但是也不是正解所以才給這個分的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.67,0:03:50.44,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.45,0:03:51.39,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.41,0:03:56.08,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為在你的答案之中完全感受不到失戀的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.83,0:03:59.16,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這份感情難以抑制無處訴說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.52,0:04:01.06,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心碎了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.16,0:04:03.15,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見 我的戀情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.58,0:04:06.46,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說你被甩了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.20,0:04:09.13,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是老師的主觀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.47,0:04:10.65,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個回答我接受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.96,0:04:16.48,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了 我知道了 好纏人啊你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.62,0:04:17.42,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好寫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.99,0:04:22.33,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水谷同學你一定還沒有瞭解失戀的痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.06,0:04:27.14,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 我被春甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.75,0:04:32.00,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你喜歡上我的時候再說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.51,0:04:36.64,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣才能讓他喜歡我呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.97,0:04:41.44,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 為什麼我會喜歡春呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.77,0:04:44.93,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 雫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.21,0:04:46.55,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師給你加分了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.76,0:04:58.19,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.59,0:04:59.80,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田春
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.73,0:05:04.58,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝…誒 捲心菜？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.65,0:05:05.46,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.51,0:05:09.65,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 對不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.72,0:05:11.69,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.91,0:05:13.72,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被狠狠的瞪了一眼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.07,0:05:18.79,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼瞪著人家就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.15,0:05:21.36,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒瞪她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.31,0:05:27.21,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得別人躲著你的原因大概就是這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.97,0:05:30.73,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你害怕了所以搞得別人也害怕起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.00,0:05:35.37,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非常喜歡你微笑的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.00,0:05:38.83,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.61,0:05:53.40,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干燒蝦仁 干燒蝦仁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.81,0:05:58.20,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田春…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.16,0:06:06.51,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非常喜歡你微笑的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.77,0:06:10.62,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常喜歡 非常喜歡 非常 非常…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.37,0:06:14.19,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.16,0:06:19.07,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.66,0:06:23.08,tk-default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚的特別節目看了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.08,0:06:23.95,tk-default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了看了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.99,0:06:25.04,tk-default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.74,0:06:24.26,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 東西掉了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.23,0:06:30.58,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝…謝謝 十分感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.69,0:06:33.03,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.33,0:06:34.82,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.39,0:06:36.47,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.17,0:06:38.13,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.09,0:06:40.29,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 那個給我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.91,0:06:41.78,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.88,0:06:45.41,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼感覺 一點都不恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.06,0:06:48.31,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.11,0:06:50.45,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔細看的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.12,0:06:53.69,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還挺帥的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.10,0:06:57.34,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是公雞 名字是名古屋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.33,0:07:02.44,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然整個人爆紅了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.75,0:07:05.13,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟春同學也挺帥的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.59,0:07:07.75,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近待人態度友善多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.98,0:07:10.39,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女生們也對他有好感了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.90,0:07:12.85,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像雫說的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.33,0:07:14.88,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要不瞪人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.94,0:07:17.40,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼也不用做 別人也會主動來搭話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.50,0:07:21.18,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是眼神的力量嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.19,0:07:21.93,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.91,0:07:24.32,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春同學 春同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.16,0:07:26.45,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以教我們功課嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.56,0:07:29.13,tk-default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關我什麼事 那種事自己做啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.46,0:07:31.52,tk-default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.59,0:07:33.92,tk-default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.08,0:07:35.65,tk-default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春同學好有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.67,0:07:36.85,tk-default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.39,0:07:29.18,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是驚人呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.23,0:07:31.28,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明和之前沒什麼變化
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.51,0:07:35.20,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到人氣暴漲之後 說什麼大家都能接受
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.98,0:07:44.36,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借寵物排解寂寞的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.14,0:07:47.57,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你在說什麼啊 夏目同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.84,0:07:49.88,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣嘛=3=
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.40,0:07:53.99,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春同學最近都被女生包圍著很難接近嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.96,0:07:56.10,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳回來 吉田
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.12,0:08:00.24,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接踢進去啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.26,0:08:02.54,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田  是相反的球門啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.67,0:08:03.45,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相反？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.80,0:08:07.07,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看這裏 看這裏 春同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.93,0:08:08.96,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田 吉田
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.25,0:08:15.36,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好玩耶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.97,0:08:20.21,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家的反應真是變化超大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.24,0:08:22.97,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明之前還沒有人敢靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.13,0:08:25.36,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去練習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.26,0:08:31.65,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小水不會是吃醋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.30,0:08:38.76,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 這就是吃醋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.17,0:08:45.22,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好坦率…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.64,0:08:55.65,tk-default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全天球技比賽 加油B班 為了勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.84,0:09:02.80,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 小水 你根本沒碰過球啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.97,0:09:05.25,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你這麼說我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.75,0:09:08.63,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到夏目同學體育是強項
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.89,0:09:13.94,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女子排球怎麼樣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.42,0:09:19.07,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果小水多動一點 或許還有機會贏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.22,0:09:20.38,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.54,0:09:22.61,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊吉田可是超級活躍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.07,0:09:25.40,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是因為太熱血 打到裁判了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.85,0:09:27.52,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？春同學呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.20,0:09:29.98,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.85,0:09:35.74,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田能一直這樣順利就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.46,0:09:39.33,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前說過的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.85,0:09:42.59,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田國中時也不來上學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.41,0:09:46.55,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年級的時候發生打架事件
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.19,0:09:49.42,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果引發了大問題
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.64,0:09:51.67,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.01,0:09:54.60,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙看起來很可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.81,0:09:56.23,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周圍的人也很怕他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.86,0:10:00.22,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件事之後 吉田就不來學校了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.05,0:10:03.20,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才說這次能順利維持就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.33,0:10:06.84,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰都有過去呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.18,0:10:10.41,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼阿佐這麼擔心春呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.13,0:10:11.55,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.19,0:10:15.48,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得你才和春說上話不久吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.54,0:10:19.69,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我欠他一份人情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.45,0:10:22.40,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.73,0:10:23.63,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味道怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.91,0:10:25.01,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.09,0:10:29.54,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師叫我們去準備器材
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.55,0:10:31.41,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？現在去？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.33,0:10:34.08,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我來做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.21,0:10:35.44,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.23,0:10:38.23,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我去做了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.52,0:10:39.74,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.75,0:10:43.03,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎 你們不是朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.79,0:10:44.87,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.08,0:10:48.31,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一個班級 沒怎麼說過話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.77,0:10:49.67,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.16,0:10:56.68,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱 好想喝水…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.89,0:10:57.23,tk-default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽好帥哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.66,0:10:58.75,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.19,0:11:01.47,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是去叫老師吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.74,0:11:03.38,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.84,0:11:05.76,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.77,0:11:08.23,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把什麼扔到別人頭上了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.46,0:11:11.03,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭腫起來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.04,0:11:12.11,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好糗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.14,0:11:13.17,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.69,0:11:16.03,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了啦 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.31,0:11:20.30,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 算了 我不想看到你 快滾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.98,0:11:23.28,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.67,0:11:28.19,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.19,0:11:32.59,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我認得你 上次闖到C班的就是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.63,0:11:36.01,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把女生打出鼻血是真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.01,0:11:39.29,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也想流鼻血試試嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.63,0:11:41.21,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.14,0:11:46.83,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別太囂張了 一年級的！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.18,0:11:54.51,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼她非要被你們這群人說「給我滾」這種話！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.07,0:11:56.95,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 打架了 打架了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.83,0:12:04.72,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 情況是不是有些不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.21,0:12:07.19,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.54,0:12:08.39,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.72,0:12:11.68,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…已經夠了吧 快停手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.89,0:12:13.37,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們道歉就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.54,0:12:17.25,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.53,0:12:40.34,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.62,0:12:45.19,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.70,0:12:48.02,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！你們幾個在幹什麼呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.86,0:13:04.93,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 怎麼能為了阻止糾紛反而將事情鬧得更大了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.44,0:13:10.12,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到竟然連我也落到被老師追著跑的地步
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.56,0:13:13.42,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.82,0:13:17.47,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哪裏做錯了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.07,0:13:20.67,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前也遇到過這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.83,0:13:24.44,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意識到的時候 周圍的人都用可怕的眼神看著我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.70,0:13:29.42,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一點都想不明白為什麼會變成那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.85,0:13:32.82,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哪裏做錯了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.24,0:13:35.46,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.35,0:13:39.14,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能說你的做法就是完全正確的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.43,0:13:44.94,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我知道春是個很善良的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.86,0:13:55.50,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.07,0:14:01.84,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道春是個很善良的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.03,0:14:06.03,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總用一天 大家一定也會知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.90,0:14:15.88,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的雫像英雄似的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.62,0:14:19.13,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英雄在我陷入危機的時候跑過來救我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.37,0:14:21.84,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陷入危機的應該是對方纔對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.05,0:14:29.00,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,額頭弄髒了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.28,0:14:46.75,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田 下一場比賽就要開始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.67,0:14:51.23,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待…待會見了 雫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.23,0:14:52.60,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…好…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.71,0:15:04.10,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是贏了比賽的話 暑假一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.93,0:15:07.68,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.00,0:15:09.74,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.55,0:15:12.23,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.22,0:15:15.85,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加…加油
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.73,0:15:26.86,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那個是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.43,0:15:32.11,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果 春贏了稱不上打賭的賭約
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.50,0:15:36.73,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目朝子 要從這麼高的地方跳下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.20,0:15:43.50,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二號吉田春 要從更高的地方跳下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.20,0:15:44.77,tk-default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家是初學者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.77,0:15:46.89,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就把目標鎖定在紅點鮭和真鱒上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.95,0:15:54.47,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魚會把從上游飄下來的餌食作為目標
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.61,0:15:56.62,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要讓魚餌這樣漂在水中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.62,0:15:57.35,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.77,0:16:01.48,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看它們游來游去的我全都抓來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.45,0:16:03.45,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是野人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.79,0:16:07.10,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼小夏目 能幫我洗一下這個鍋嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.12,0:16:08.13,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.75,0:16:17.49,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.25,0:16:21.06,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊 溪流垂釣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.64,0:16:26.76,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿三哥和春是表兄弟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.55,0:16:31.51,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊是啊 這傢伙的老爸是我老媽的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.96,0:16:36.02,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為高中離我家比較近 今年開始就借住在我那了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.34,0:16:37.29,tk-default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.60,0:16:38.35,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.47,0:16:40.11,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小水知道這些事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.38,0:16:41.51,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 完全不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.74,0:16:44.14,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還一直以為是親哥哥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.28,0:16:45.88,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.94,0:16:47.60,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的哥哥另有其人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.25,0:16:50.12,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 說起他那個哥哥啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.91,0:16:50.54,tk-default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿三哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.17,0:16:54.25,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要一個勁地亂說多餘的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.73,0:17:16.81,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春 春
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.52,0:17:21.46,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒醒 已經回到店裏了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.95,0:17:23.37,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把行李拿下來 快起來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.05,0:17:26.80,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經把春叫醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.91,0:17:28.49,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是睡了好久呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.49,0:17:30.35,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.95,0:17:33.93,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.08,0:17:36.81,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.39,0:17:42.20,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我去把特產分一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.34,0:17:43.92,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在店裏稍等下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.92,0:17:45.64,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.92,0:17:50.40,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 最近新建了一個交友網站哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.97,0:17:55.30,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真傷心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.71,0:17:59.99,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一見到人家就跑開 真是太誇張了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.89,0:18:05.17,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿佐同學 這個人是之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.82,0:18:08.19,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搶阿三哥錢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.17,0:18:13.59,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才春突然逃了出來…原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.91,0:18:19.74,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿善 我貌似被誤認為從你那裏搶錢了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.87,0:18:22.68,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是春同學的哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.05,0:18:26.50,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫吉田優山 春給大家添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.83,0:18:30.29,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 他就是白天說的春的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.63,0:18:32.98,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便提一句 是我借了人家錢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.03,0:18:36.85,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…你把西瓜切開了嗎 我還想玩砸西瓜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.00,0:18:38.18,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不會玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.51,0:18:43.55,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 想不到春居然有這麼多朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.89,0:18:47.32,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 那傢伙表現還不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.63,0:18:48.72,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.15,0:18:52.76,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了水谷同學 還來上學了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.25,0:18:54.93,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒幫什麼忙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.82,0:18:57.58,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.33,0:19:11.11,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 那傢伙是個笨蛋 請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.23,0:19:15.86,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 春同學為什麼會逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.01,0:19:19.39,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件事啊 很平常啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.64,0:19:21.43,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他是個嚴重的兄控
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.59,0:19:26.62,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還以為吉田的哥哥是什麼人物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.03,0:19:29.08,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意外的是個普通的善良人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.67,0:19:32.13,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還要買東西 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.24,0:19:33.05,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.18,0:19:34.48,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.44,0:19:41.37,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.06,0:19:46.56,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見 今後春也拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.62,0:19:54.45,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得是個怪哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.71,0:19:58.61,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然趕不上弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.03,0:20:01.18,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這麼慢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.18,0:20:05.15,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是啊 為什麼老做些對人家心臟不好的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.82,0:20:07.80,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那傢伙一起玩了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.96,0:20:08.70,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.98,0:20:11.30,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起玩砸西瓜了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.81,0:20:16.63,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙一直幽怨地悶在這裏想著砸西瓜的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.95,0:20:19.27,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.66,0:20:20.59,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.54,0:20:24.34,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 放開我 會疼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.22,0:20:30.21,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哥哥說…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.44,0:20:33.08,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是嚴重的兄控
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.08,0:20:34.60,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.05,0:20:37.73,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那為什麼要躲著他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.64,0:20:41.81,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為討厭他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.99,0:20:43.77,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭? 為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.54,0:20:47.85,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多管閒事 別什麼事都問
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.12,0:20:50.88,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.91,0:21:04.64,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.10,0:21:10.99,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是生氣要走嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.31,0:21:13.93,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 確實如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.23,0:21:18.71,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我家也有西瓜 要砸嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.80,0:21:26.70,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砸好了雫 下一個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.81,0:21:28.32,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.32,0:21:29.58,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還以為自己很瞭解他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.98,0:21:32.22,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果卻發現自己對他幾乎一無所知
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.73,0:21:34.51,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別什麼事都問
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.68,0:21:39.72,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底發生了什麼 讓他露出那麼可怕的神情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.91,0:21:40.82,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.92,0:21:44.71,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 剛才說了那樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.55,0:21:46.72,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.34,0:21:52.33,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雫總會幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.29,0:21:57.09,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該回報你一下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.04,0:21:58.72,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約會
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.23,0:22:02.52,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那和我約會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.51,0:22:07.20,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個 可以倒是可以
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.64,0:22:10.91,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 這個…總覺得有點不對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.25,0:22:13.17,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砸西瓜是這樣玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.21,0:22:14.99,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.01,0:22:18.88,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道的事 以後知道了就好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.54,0:22:20.92,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.96,0:24:02.04,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田 你一對著鏡頭就緊張過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.45,0:24:03.32,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
